dc_title_s: Passaic Valley Sewerage Commission, map showing riparian grants compiled from official maps of the New Jersey Riparian Commission
dc_description_s: Map by the Passaic Valley Sewerage Commission showing the riparian grants to various local properties and businesses along the Passaic River. Includes schedule of 90 freeholder's licenses.|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection|Date is taken from most recent on map
